{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-13728/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-13728"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:37:28"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A shot of a man and woman walking down a staircase is overlaid with a shot of snow falling."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-13728","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-13728"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1/a389ce33-ad7f-4ef3-87a0-fe6d4369a269","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:10:59.704Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma is repeatedly associated with red and green. Consider, for example, her <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW158652808 BCX2\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01247.html\"><u>red</u></a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW158652808 BCX2\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-04039.html\"><u>green</u></a> dresses and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW158652808 BCX2\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-04733.html\"><u>green</u></a> shirt.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:692.7272727272727,400.5194805194805,257.1428571428571,570.3896103896102"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1/7a0b3dba-7853-4fc5-9a4b-8c1cf4f874b0","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:11:30.672Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Omar P.L. Moore suggests that in certain scenes the “haunting occuring [sic] throughout ‘Phantom Thread’ and [that] is evoked in the title is the suggestion of a third presence (not necessarily Cyril) but a third presence that often exists within the frame when Alma and Reynolds are in it” (Moore, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW180518749 BCX2\" href=\"https://popcornreel.com/htm/phantomessay2.html\"><u>A Boy’s Best Friend</u></a>”). That “phantom” is seen here in the fresco and in the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW180518749 BCX2\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-03215.html\"><u>shot</u></a> of Reynolds and Alma walking down a street.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13728/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:201.0389610389609,125.4545454545454,1154.805194805195,486.23376623376635"}}}]}]}]}